                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Ability to handle multiple projects simultaneously.</li>
                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Functional knowledge of basic front-end development (HTML, CSS, and Javascript).</li>
                </ul>
                <ul>
                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Firm understanding of the latest and legacy browser capabilities, including mobile.</li>
                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Team player, demonstrates the ability to receive and apply feedback and input for direction as well as provide constructive feedback to others.</li>
                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Familiarity with project planning software, such as Basecamp.</li>
                    <li class="jobs-bullet">Excellent ability to think on your feet. Demonstrates strong analytical problem-solving skills across a variety of contexts.</li>
